title: Quintessa Swindell, a Trans and Nonbinary Star of DC’s ‘Black Adam’
description: “My trans and nonbinary identity is the thing that I’m the most confident about in my life,” Mx. Swindell said.
dc:creator: Alex Hawgood
media:credit: Jingyu Lin for The New York Times
media:description: Quintessa Swindell is one of the few transgender actors to star in a big-budget DC film.
